### 管理員商品 API 測試示例

### 1. 創建商品
POST http://localhost:3000/api/admin/products
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "高級辦公椅",
  "subtitle": "人體工學設計，舒適耐用",
  "description": "這是一款專為長時間辦公設計的高級人體工學椅，採用高品質網布和記憶棉，提供卓越的支撐和舒適度。",
  "image": "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1586023492125-27b2c045efd7",
  "unit": "張",
  "spec": "尺寸：60x60x110cm\n材質：網布、記憶棉、鋁合金\n顏色：黑色、灰色\n承重：150kg",
  "isFeatured": true,
  "startDate": "2026-02-08T00:00:00Z",
  "endDate": "2026-02-28T23:59:59Z",
  "priceTiers": [
    {
      "minQty": 1,
      "price": 2999
    },
    {
      "minQty": 5,
      "price": 2799
    },
    {
      "minQty": 10,
      "price": 2599
    },
    {
      "minQty": 20,
      "price": 2399
    }
  ]
}

### 2. 獲取管理員商品列表
GET http://localhost:3000/api/admin/products?page=1&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 3. 獲取特定商品詳情（管理員版本）
GET http://localhost:3000/api/admin/products/{{productId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 4. 更新商品
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/admin/products/{{productId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "高級人體工學辦公椅（升級版）",
  "isFeatured": false,
  "priceTiers": [
    {
      "minQty": 1,
      "price": 2899
    },
    {
      "minQty": 5,
      "price": 2699
    },
    {
      "minQty": 10,
      "price": 2499
    },
    {
      "minQty": 20,
      "price": 2299
    },
    {
      "minQty": 50,
      "price": 2099
    }
  ]
}

### 5. 刪除商品（軟刪除）
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/admin/products/{{productId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 6. 測試錯誤場景：未授權訪問
GET http://localhost:3000/api/admin/products
# 不提供 Authorization header

### 7. 測試錯誤場景：普通會員訪問
GET http://localhost:3000/api/admin/products
Authorization: Bearer {{memberToken}}

### 8. 測試錯誤場景：無效數據
POST http://localhost:3000/api/admin/products
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "",
  "unit": "",
  "priceTiers": []
}

### 9. 測試錯誤場景：重複的價格階梯
POST http://localhost:3000/api/admin/products
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "測試商品",
  "unit": "個",
  "priceTiers": [
    {
      "minQty": 1,
      "price": 100
    },
    {
      "minQty": 1,
      "price": 90
    }
  ]
}

### 10. 測試錯誤場景：無效的時間範圍
POST http://localhost:3000/api/admin/products
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "測試商品",
  "unit": "個",
  "startDate": "2026-02-28T00:00:00Z",
  "endDate": "2026-02-08T00:00:00Z",
  "priceTiers": [
    {
      "minQty": 1,
      "price": 100
    }
  ]
}